// =============================================================================
// EcoReport Specification — alternative to a fat repository
//
// USE WHEN: you have many query variants of the same entity (e.g. "reports
// pending verification in district X", "reports overdue SLA", "reports by
// reporter in last 30 days") and you don't want a repository with 15 methods.
//
// HOW IT WORKS: a Specification carries the filter + includes + ordering
// for one query shape. The handler composes specs with IApplicationDbContext
// via an extension method.
//
// PLACEHOLDERS:
//   __ENTITY__   — PascalCase singular, e.g. Report
//   __SPEC__     — PascalCase descriptive name, e.g. PendingVerificationInDistrict
// =============================================================================


